{"tid":1812244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[廣傳] 請肺炎病人到 澳門 / 大灣區 / 上海 治病","createTime":"2020-01-05T10:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T10:51:18.000Z","uid":49784,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f69d26d67bcb4a9dd4d8fb78df57520d198e5487","tid":1812244,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:34:37.000Z","msg":"呢幾個地方已經超越左香港<br />\n中招同胞去就近嘅 澳門 / 大灣區 /上海 治病<br />\n呢三個地方平價，質素高<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認同請分享</span></span><br />\n<br />\n廣藥集團近日正式進軍澳門<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2345863/廣藥進軍澳門布局國際\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2345863%2F%E5%BB%A3%E8%97%A5%E9%80%B2%E8%BB%8D%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1S9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=7897960c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2345863/廣藥進軍澳門布局國際</a><br />\n<br />\n澳門回歸十五周年後，各方面發展水準都已超越香港。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/notes/正思香港/一比嚇一跳澳門和香港驚人差距/1302911689804701/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fnotes%2F%E6%AD%A3%E6%80%9D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%2F%E4%B8%80%E6%AF%94%E5%9A%87%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%B3%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E5%92%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%A9%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%AE%E8%B7%9D%2F1302911689804701%2F&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1S9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=c25c0da5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/notes/正思香港/一比嚇一跳澳門和香港驚人差距/1302911689804701/</a><br />\n<br />\n全球城市競爭力 香港遭上海超越<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20191116/mobile/odn-20191116-1116_00176_039.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191116%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20191116-1116_00176_039.html&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1S9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=491e5447\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20191116/mobile/odn-20191116-1116_00176_039.html</a><br />\n<br />\n連香港人都咁講（自己決定入唔入呢條link)<br />\n對不起香港人, 我要說實話, 上海已經超越香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/m.discuss.com.hk/amp_viewthread.php%3ftid=28735042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fm.discuss.com.hk%2Famp_viewthread.php%253ftid%3D28735042&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1S9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=b0940709\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/m.discuss.com.hk/amp_viewthread.php%3ftid=28735042</a><br />\n<br />\nAXA 安盛拓大灣區保險醫療服務<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.capital-hk.com/2019/05/21/axa-安盛拓大灣區保險醫療服務/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.capital-hk.com%2F2019%2F05%2F21%2Faxa-%E5%AE%89%E7%9B%9B%E6%8B%93%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA%E9%86%AB%E7%99%82%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%2F&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1S9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=7389a7b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.capital-hk.com/2019/05/21/axa-安盛拓大灣區保險醫療服務/</a><br />\n<br />\n大灣區建設是國家戰略，醫療健康服務是大灣區建設的核心內容之一<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.capital-hk.com/2018/11/21/粵港澳大灣區共同體：醫療協作平台成立%E3%80%80打通大/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.capital-hk.com%2F2018%2F11%2F21%2F%E7%B2%B5%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E9%AB%94%EF%BC%9A%E9%86%AB%E7%99%82%E5%8D%94%E4%BD%9C%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%25E3%2580%2580%E6%89%93%E9%80%9A%E5%A4%A7%2F&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1S9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=b63789b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.capital-hk.com/2018/11/21/粵港澳大灣區共同體：醫療協作平台成立%E3%80%80打通大/</a><br />\n<br />\n相反香港嘅醫院其實質素唔係幾好<br />\nd 病床成日爆，瞓走廊床又有，冇位瞓又有<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">精明嘅大家，記得推廣比大眾</span></span>"},{"pid":"b376c48acf0b49f1cba3101eae35751a41e40029","tid":1812244,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:35:30.000Z","msg":"【警告】今個新年 屯門水貨客問題特別嚴重<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1812239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1812239</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1cce38838b71deb5fcb2e7201fdedacf629cef0c","tid":1812244,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:38:15.000Z","msg":"香港好多醫療失誤，大家記得叫d 親戚去<br />\n<br />\n非香港地區，非香港醫院 醫病<br />\n<br />\n救得一個得一個<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳"},{"pid":"7bd9a4f3543aaaa959c592b1cc57acb259e0ee23","tid":1812244,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:38:47.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a7ac452f35c08da455db92e7bd9e2abc15ea85c5","tid":1812244,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:40:14.000Z","msg":"刻不容緩"},{"pid":"b604043eeee38e09ce7916d46b0883751461c855","tid":1812244,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50ddc70829410776a56e575f52217677f339613","tid":1812244,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T10:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}